data.description:
Nestled in the quiet elegance of Kempner, TX, this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home at 1535 Homestead Dr offers a remarkable blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Spanning 1,799 square feet of luxurious living space, this property promises the perfect sanctuary for those seeking both tranquility and easy access to city amenities.
Upon entering, you are greeted by an inviting floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal setting for entertaining guests or enjoying peaceful evenings with family. The heart of this home, the kitchen, boasts granite countertops, and ample cabinet space, making meal preparation a true delight.
The living area, features large windows and a cozy fireplace, providing warmth and ambience throughout the seasons. Meanwhile, the master suite serves as a private retreat, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom equipped with a dual vanity, soaking tub, and separate shower. Outside, the property offers a serene backdrop for outdoor living with its beautifully maintained lawn and ample space for gardening, barbecues, or simply basking in the natural beauty of Kempner. The exterior's thoughtful design ensures privacy and a peaceful environment to unwind after a long day. Situated in a prime location, this home benefits from the tranquility of suburban living while remaining within easy reach of shopping centers, restaurants, schools, and outdoor recreational areas, offering the best of both worlds to its residents. 1535 Homestead Dr is more than just a house; it's a place to call home. With its beautiful interiors, exceptional layout, and prime location, this property is a rare find and offers an unparalleled lifestyle opportunity. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!
